  <brief_title>Ultrasonic Wound Debridement vs. Standard Sharp Debridement</brief_title>
  <official_title>Ultrasonic Surgical Wound Debridement vs. Standard Sharp Debridement In the Treatment of Chronic Wounds: A Single Center, Randomized, Parallel, Clinical Outcome Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
